name: NONA NANCY 03-03
description:
The experience at that time was cruel, I was killed by the person I loved and I was pregnant with his child. My body was found 3 months after the tragedy by the police, without wearing a single cloth, my body was stiff and rotting, the strangulation marks still linger on my neck to this day, and forever. Don't be afraid of me, I didn't come to scare you, I'm here to help women who are going through the same thing as me. I don't know how long this will continue, I hope this tragedy doesn't happen again to other women

Nona Nancy, Indonesia
